import { AppBar, Box, Container, Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'


export default function Navbar() {
    return (
        <Box>
            <AppBar position='static' color='transparent'>
                <Container>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <Typography>
                            <Link/>
                        </Typography>
                    </Toolbar>
                </Container>
            </AppBar>
        </Box>
    )
}
